00:02:08.300 --> 00:02:10.860
 We are what we think. 

00:02:11.300 --> 00:02:15.600
 If we want to have a happy and healthy life, 

00:02:15.840 --> 00:02:20.140
 we must change the way we think about the positive pole. 

00:02:20.620 --> 00:02:24.380
 There are people who use the power of the spirit to heal, 

00:02:24.660 --> 00:02:33.120
 others to invent machines, ships and all kinds of enterprises for the good of humanity. 

00:02:33.320 --> 00:02:39.440
 But on the other hand, there are also people who use the spirit to harm themselves and others. 

00:02:39.680 --> 00:02:44.740
 The spirit was symbolized by ancient scholars by a donkey. 

00:02:45.400 --> 00:02:50.100
 because he sometimes behaves like a donkey. 

00:02:50.500 --> 00:02:53.780
 Recall the fable of the "Assess of Apuleius". 

00:02:54.160 --> 00:03:00.840
