00:03:01.100 --> 00:03:04.640
 entered Jerusalem mounted on a donkey 

00:03:04.960 --> 00:03:07.840
 and he was acclaimed by the multitudes. 

00:03:08.160 --> 00:03:10.680
 The teaching that the Grand Master gave to humanity was: 

00:03:10.920 --> 00:03:15.960
 "I am the master and lord of my spirit and he serves all my purposes" 

00:03:16.440 --> 00:03:19.540
 In truth, the vast majority of human beings 

00:03:19.540 --> 00:03:22.940
 wear this donkey on his shoulders. 

00:03:23.240 --> 00:03:30.180
 The mind needs a direction that could turn it into an extraordinary tool. 

00:03:30.740 --> 00:03:35.480
 This direction would be in the account of our soul. 

